{"article_id":"16FboDgo9QTWgBGb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The unemployment rate is up at 8.2 percent ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"reports the Labor Department .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Unemployment up ;","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"69K jobs added","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Republicans quickly seized on anemic jobs number","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"released Friday","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"to press the case","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that it ' s time for a change in the White House ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"with GOP presidential nominee Mitt Romney saying ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"\" It is now clear to everyone","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that President Obama ' s policies have failed to achieve their goals . \"","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"A recovery","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that looked strong at the start of the year","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"sputtered last month ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"with the economy adding a mere 69,000 jobs in May","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"- well below expectations of 150,000 new jobs -","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"and the unemployment rate ticking up slightly to 8.2 percent ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"the Labor Department reported .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"The May numbers capped a stunning reversal from monthly reports of more than 200,000 new jobs","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"as the headwinds of Europe and a broader global slowdown have struck the U.S. economy .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The disappointing data put Democrats on the defensive","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"and undermined a key talking point by President Barack Obama of an economy slowly but steadily on the mend , a crucial argument","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"as he faces Romney ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"who is focusing his campaign squarely on the president ' s handling of the economy .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"\" The Obama economy is crushing America ' s middle class , \"","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Romney said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" Today ' s weak jobs report is devastating news for American workers and American families , \"","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"\" This week has seen a cascade of one bad piece of economic news after another .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Slowing GDP growth , plunging consumer confidence , an increase in unemployment claims , and now another dismal jobs report all stand as a harsh indictment of the President ' s handling of the economy . \"","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Obama blamed the dismal numbers on challenges","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"posed by Europe","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"and the spike in gasoline prices earlier this year ,","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"yet stressed","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"that the true roadblock are House Republicans","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"who have refused to pass measures","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"to improve infrastructure ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"boost local government employment , back tax breaks","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"to help hiring","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"and clean energy ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"and refinance mortgages at cheaper rates for homeowners .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"\" Now is not the time","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"to play politics , \"","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Obama said in an afternoon speech in Golden Valley , Minn.","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"\" Now is not the time","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"to sit on your hands .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"The American people expect their leaders to work hard","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"no matter what year it is . \"","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"Just as the president tries to shift the burden onto Capitol Hill ,","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"Romney directed it back to the White House ,","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"brushing off claims","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"that global turmoil was dragging down the economy .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"\" This has been going on for a lot longer than the crisis in the euro , \"","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"he told CNBC in an interview .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"\" Jobs are job one for the presidency .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"And this president instead put in place Obamacare ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"his own team concluded","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"would slow the recovery","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and it has .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"He decided","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"instead of getting people back to work","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"he ' d fight for something","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"he thought","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"was historic . \"","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"MSNBC ' s Chuck Todd summed up Obama ' s challenge on Friday morning","depth":3},{"id":66,"text":"when he called the data \" a stomach punch to the White House . \"","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":133,"left":107,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":96,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":70,"right":95,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":68,"right":69,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":68,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":76,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":73,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":71,"right":72,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":8,"right":74,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":94,"left":84,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pa